subtitle: This Month’s Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (June 17 - July 16) will also receive:

— The new Överflöd Suzume (Super)
— 30% off the new Hands On Car Wash
— Double Rewards on Money Laundering
— 50% off all HSW Upgrades
— The Magnetics Bomber Zipped and Track Pants
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
